    • Method Detail

      • add

        boolean add(PeriodIF period,
            PointIF startPoint,
            PointIF endPoint)
        Append this 'MovingPoint' object by a further movement section defined by the passed values.
        Creates an appropriate unit object and append this to this object.
        Parameters:
        period - - time period of this movement section
        startPoint - - point at the beginning of the movement for this period
        endPoint - - point at the end of the movement for this period
        Returns:
        true if the adding was successful, false otherwise
